	(260, '_transient_rss_4f99f27f6c650fb00d8695f4fb36094e', 'O:9:"MagpieRSS":19:{s:6:"parser";i:0;s:12:"current_item";a:0:{}s:5:"items";a:30:{i:0;a:14:{s:5:"title";s:60:"Tumblr & Deviantart Added To jQuery Social Media Tabs Plugin";s:4:"link";s:61:"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/DesignChemical/~3/bZc0NnOC_hE/";s:8:"comments";s:131:"http://www.designchemical.com/blog/index.php/wordpress-plugins/tumblr-deviantart-added-to-jquery-social-media-tabs-plugin/#comments";s:7:"pubdate";s:31:"Mon, 28 May 2012 04:48:26 +0000";s:2:"dc";a:1:{s:7:"creator";s:3:"Lee";}s:8:"category";s:70:"Wordpress PluginsdeviantartjQuerypluginssocial networkstumblrwordpress";s:4:"guid";s:42:"http://www.designchemical.com/blog/?p=3408";s:11:"description";s:574:"<p>Starting with versions 1.4 both the jQuery Social Media Tabs &#038; the Social Network Tabs For WordPress plugins now include Tumblr and Deviantart tabs giving a total of 15 social networks supported with 33 feed options.</p>\n<p>The Tumblr feed includes specific styling and formatting for all tumblr content types &#8211; photo, video, regular, quote, audio, conversation &#038; link, including an  &#8230; <a href="http://www.designchemical.com/blog/index.php/wordpress-plugins/tumblr-deviantart-added-to-jquery-social-media-tabs-plugin/" class="read_more">more</a></p>";s:7:"content";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";s:3237:"<p>Starting with versions 1.4 both the <a href="http://www.designchemical.com/blog/index.php/premium-jquery-plugins/jquery-social-media-tabs-plugin/" class="underline">jQuery Social Media Tabs</a> &#038; the <a href="http://www.designchemical.com/blog/index.php/premium-wordpress-plugins/premium-wordpress-plugin-social-network-tabs/" class="underline">Social Network Tabs For WordPress</a> plugins now include Tumblr and Deviantart tabs giving a total of 15 social networks supported with 33 feed options.</p>\n<p>The Tumblr feed includes specific styling and formatting for all tumblr content types &#8211; photo, video, regular, quote, audio, conversation &#038; link, including an inline video player for video posts and options for setting thumbnail and video player width.</p>\n<p>Other updates to both plugins include:</p>\n<ul class="content-list">\n<li>Added option to show tweets from a twitter list</li>\n<li>Option to display twitter profile avatar image in each tweet</li>\n<li>Option to display complete text &#038; images for both facebook and RSS feed posts</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Latest versions now available from codecanyon</p>\n<ul class="content-list">\n<li><a href="http://codecanyon.net/item/social-network-tabs-for-wordpress/1982987?ref=designchemical" rel="nofollow" class="external underline">Social Network Tabs For WordPress</a></li>\n<li><a href="http://codecanyon.net/item/jquery-social-media-tabs/1932796" rel="nofollow" class="external underline">jQuery Social Media Tabs</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Plugin Demo Sites</h3>\n<p><a href="http://www.designchemical.com/blog/index.php/premium-wordpress-plugins/premium-wordpress-plugin-social-network-tabs/" class="underline">Social Network Tabs For WordPress</a></p>\n<p><a href="http://www.designchemical.com/blog/index.php/premium-jquery-plugins/jquery-social-media-tabs-plugin/" class="underline">jQuery Social Media Tabs</a></p>\n<div class="feedflare">\n<a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?a=bZc0NnOC_hE:9bf-k_mfJdo:V_sGLiPBpWU"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?i=bZc0NnOC_hE:9bf-k_mfJdo:V_sGLiPBpWU" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?a=bZc0NnOC_hE:9bf-k_mfJdo:F7zBnMyn0Lo"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?i=bZc0NnOC_hE:9bf-k_mfJdo:F7zBnMyn0Lo" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?a=bZc0NnOC_hE:9bf-k_mfJdo:gIN9vFwOqvQ"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?i=bZc0NnOC_hE:9bf-k_mfJdo:gIN9vFwOqvQ" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?a=bZc0NnOC_hE:9bf-k_mfJdo: