dPress</a> plugins now include Tumblr and Deviantart tabs giving a total of 15 social networks supported with 33 feed options.</p>\n<p>The Tumblr feed includes specific styling and formatting for all tumblr content types &#8211; photo, video, regular, quote, audio, conversation &#038; link, including an inline video player for video posts and options for setting thumbnail and video player width.</p>\n<p>Other updates to both plugins include:</p>\n<ul class="content-list">\n<li>Added option to show tweets from a twitter list</li>\n<li>Option to display twitter profile avatar image in each tweet</li>\n<li>Option to display complete text &#038; images for both facebook and RSS feed posts</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Latest versions now available from codecanyon</p>\n<ul class="content-list">\n<li><a href="http://codecanyon.net/item/social-network-tabs-for-wordpress/1982987?ref=designchemical" rel="nofollow" class="external underline">Social Network Tabs For WordPress</a></li>\n<li><a href="http://codecanyon.net/item/jquery-social-media-tabs/1932796" rel="nofollow" class="external underline">jQuery Social Media Tabs</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Plugin Demo Sites</h3>\n<p><a href="http://www.designchemical.com/blog/index.php/premium-wordpress-plugins/premium-wordpress-plugin-social-network-tabs/" class="underline">Social Network Tabs For WordPress</a></p>\n<p><a href="http://www.designchemical.com/blog/index.php/premium-jquery-plugins/jquery-social-media-tabs-plugin/" class="underline">jQuery Social Media Tabs</a></p>\n<div class="feedflare">\n<a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?a=bZc0NnOC_hE:9bf-k_mfJdo:V_sGLiPBpWU"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?i=bZc0NnOC_hE:9bf-k_mfJdo:V_sGLiPBpWU" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?a=bZc0NnOC_hE:9bf-k_mfJdo:F7zBnMyn0Lo"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?i=bZc0NnOC_hE:9bf-k_mfJdo:F7zBnMyn0Lo" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburn