ss-packing-segment/&amp;media=http://www.wendyslookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/Packing-15-650x433.jpg&amp;description=Up%20in%20the%20Air%20::%20Comfy%20maxi%20dress%20&amp;layout=horizontal" frameborder="0" scrolling="no" width="320" height="240"></iframe></div>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nFor blazers, I turn one of the arms inside out and fold it into the other arm to keep its shape.\r\n\r\n<img title="Packing-10" src="http://www.wendyslookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/Packing-10-433x650.jpg" alt="" width="433" height="650" />\r\n<div id="pinit_12"><iframe src="http://pinit-cdn.pinterest.com/pinit.html?url=http://www.wendyslookbook.com/2012/06/up-in-the-air-comfy-maxi-dress-packing-segment/&amp;media=http://www.wendyslookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/Packing-10-433x650.jpg&amp;description=Up%20in%20the%20Air%20::%20Comfy%20maxi%20dress%20&amp;layout=horizontal" frameborder="0" scrolling="no" width="320" height="240"></iframe></div>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<img title="Packing-11" src="http://www.wendyslookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/Packing-11-433x650.jpg" alt="" width="433" height="650" />\r\n<div id="pinit_13"><iframe src="http://pinit-cdn.pinterest.com/pinit.html?url=http://www.wendyslookbook.com/2012/06/up-in-the-air-comfy-maxi-dress-packing-segment/&amp;media=http://www.wendyslookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/Packing-11-433x650.jpg&amp;description=Up%20in%20the%20Air%20::%20Comfy%20maxi%20dress%20&amp;layout=horizontal" frameborder="0" scrolling="no" width="320" height="240"></iframe></div>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nEverything laid out…\r\n\r\n<img title="Packing-13" src="http://www.wendyslookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/Packing-13-433x650.jpg" alt="" width="433" height="650" />\r\n<div id="pinit_14"><iframe src="http://pinit-cdn.pinterest.com/pinit.html?url=http://www.wendyslookbook.com/2012/06/up-in-the-air-comfy-maxi-dress-packing-segment/&amp;media=http://www.wendyslookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/Packing-13-433x650.jpg&amp;description=Up%20in%20the%20Air%20::%20Comfy%20maxi%20dress%20&amp;layout=horizontal" frameborder="0" scrolling="no" width="320" height="240"></iframe></div>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nAnd packed into one luggage…\r\n\r\n<img title="Packing-14" src="http://www.wendyslookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/Packing-14-433x650.jpg" alt="" width="433" height="650" />\r\n<div id="pinit_15"><iframe src="http://pinit-cdn.pinterest.com/pinit.html?url=http://www.wendyslookbook.com/2012/06/up-in-the-air-comfy-maxi-dress-packing-segment/&amp;media=http://www.wendyslookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/Packing-14-433x650.jpg&amp;description=Up%20in%20the%20Air%20::%20Comfy%20maxi%20dress%20&amp;layout=horizontal" frameborder="0" scrolling="no" width="320" height="240"></iframe></div>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nNo carry-on needed.  Olive sitting pretty and ready to go!  =)\r\n\r\n<img title="Packing-17" src="http://www.wendyslookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/Packing-17-433x650.jpg" alt="" width="433" height="650" />\r\n<div id="pinit_16"><iframe src="http://pinit-cdn.pinterest.com/pinit.html?url=http://www.wendyslookbook.com/2012/06/up-in-the-air-comfy-maxi-dress-packing-segment/&amp;media=http://www.wendyslookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/Packing-17-433x650.jpg&amp;description=Up%20in%20the%20Air%20::%20Comfy%20maxi%20dress%20&amp;layout=horizontal" frameborder="0" scrolling="no" width="320" height="240"></iframe></div>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nThank you so much for letting me share my travel/packing segment with you!  I hope it was helpful.  And moreover, thank you for being on this journey with me.  A few years ago while sitting at my desk analyzing financial statements, I never ever thought I would get a chance to travel to Italy for a fashion related event.  Sitting here on the plane, I still can’t believe it.  Thank you for your support and encouragement.  I truly appreciate it.  I hope you’re having a wonderful weekend so far and talk to you soon!\r\n\r\n:: Outfit ::\r\n\r\nMaxi dress :: Forever 